'''Akosombo-Tema Highway''' is the major highway that joins the industrial and port city of [[Tema]] to electricity generating town of [[Akosombo]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://allafrica.com/stories/201601221779.html|title=Ghana: Tema Motorway Roundabout Traffic Jam to Ease Soon - Nadmo, Assemblies, NGO to Proffer Solution|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://citifmonline.com/2015/04/03/two-police-officers-perish-near-shai-hills/|title=Two police officers perish near Shai-Hills|first=Efua Idan|last=Osam|date=3 April 2015|publisher=}}</ref> The highway connects three regions of [[Ghana]], the [[Greater Accra Region]], the [[Eastern Region (Ghana)|Eastern Region]] and the [[Volta Region]].

